<h3 class="wp-block-heading" id="Cable-Reverse-Grip-Tricep-Pushdown">Cable Reverse-Grip Tricep Pushdown</h3>



<p>The <a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/cable-reverse-grip-tricep-pushdown" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">cable reverse-grip tricep pushdown</a> combines the foundational pushdown movement with a reverse bar grip. This exercise primarily targets the triceps medial heads, with the long and lateral heads as secondary movers.</p>



<p>Because of this, you get an exercise that promotes well-rounded tricep development. Using the cable machine offers resistance throughout the full range of motion.</p>



